documents.name: Privacy policy
documents.text:
Privacy Policy

FileInfo takes your privacy seriously. We do not sell or redistribute any personal information. The FileInfo website does not collect or store information about individual users.

Cookies

Quizzes and advertisements served on FileInfo.com may place and read cookies within your web browser or use web beacons to collect information. You may choose to limit the cookies you accept by modifying your browser's security preferences.

Google may use DART cookies, which allow targeted ads to be served to your web browser. To learn more about the information Google collects and how to control your privacy settings, view the Google Privacy Policy.

Questions

If you have questions regarding this privacy policy, please contact FileInfo.

documents.text:
Terms of Use Usage Policy

You may use this website for the intended purpose of learning about file types and software programs. You may not use any kind of automatic device or program to access or copy any portion of FileInfo.com.

Website Content

All content found on FileInfo.com is property of Sharpened Productions. Information on this website is provided as a public reference, without any warranties, and is delivered on an "as-is" and "as-available" basis. Each file extension entry and software page is verified before being published on FileInfo.com. While every effort is made to ensure the accuracy of information provided on this website, FileInfo.com is not responsible for incorrect information. Please contact FileInfo with any possible errors.

Copyright Information

All information found on this website is original, copyrighted content of Sharpened Productions. Additionally, all webpage text, HTML code, web scripts, database information, images, and page design is original content and is protected by international copyright law. You may use information from the FileInfo website for personal use, but you may not republish, reproduce, upload, post, or publicly distribute content found on this website. If you wish to include information from FileInfo.com in a paper or publication, please submit a written request.

Icon images displayed on FileInfo are used solely for representative purposes. These images retain the copyright of the respective software developers and may not copied and republished. Developers with questions about displaying icons on the FileInfo.com website may contact us.

Please report all copyright violations to FileInfo.

Privacy Policy

FileInfo does not collect or redistribute personal information. View the full privacy policy.

Linking Policy

You may link to FileInfo (https://fileinfo.com/) without seeking permission. However, adult websites, offensive websites, and any other websites not appropriate for all age groups may not link to FileInfo.com. If you would like to use an image to link to FileInfo, you may use the image below:

Visit the Help Center for more information about linking to FileInfo.com.

Questions?

Please address all questions regarding usage of this website to the FileInfo administrator.
